.DT
query_item
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_item

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_item -  This method will return an array of the information associated with the item.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed query_item(string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the item to query
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the item array as detailed above.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/gathering.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method will return an array of the information associated with
the item.  The array consists of:

.EP
.SP 5 5
  ({
.EP
.SP 5 5
     skill,       // skill needed to find this item   (string)
.EP
.SP 5 5
     difficulty,  // taskmaster difficulty            (int)
.EP
.SP 5 5
     upper,       // taskmaster "upper" parameter     (int)
.EP
.SP 5 5
     extra,       // taskmaster "extra" parameter     (mixed)
.EP
.SP 5 5
     season,      // available season(s)              (string *)
.EP
.SP 5 5
     quant,       // quantity (int or (int)(:\<code\>:)) (mixed)
.EP
.SP 5 5
     ob           // filename of object to be created (string)
.EP
.SP 5 5
   })
.EP
.SP 5 5

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_item()

.EP

